      "body" : "Note that <code>SimpleDateFormat</code> is configured with a <code>TimeZone</code> either by default or by calling the <code>setTimeZone</code> method. That time zone is used during parsing <i>if and only if</i> a time zone is not indicated in the string to be parsed."
